author: Emma Elsworthy
title: 'Restrictions are working': Five new coronavirus cases confirmed in NSW
description: NSW Premier Gladys Berejiklian confirms just five new cases of coronavirus in NSW over the last 24 hours, bringing the state's total to 2,980.
content:
Updated 
April 23, 2020 08:29:06
NSW Premier Gladys Berejiklian has confirmed just five new cases of coronavirus in NSW, bringing the state's total to 2,980.
